---
<section class="section" id="roadmap">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg></div>
      <h2>Roadmap</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot timeline-dot--done"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <span class="timeline-tag timeline-tag--done">Done</span>
        <h3>Foundation</h3>
        <p>Glioblastoma corpus processed. Knowledge graph operational. First contradictions identified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot timeline-dot--active"></div>
        <span class="timeline-tag timeline-tag--active">Active</span>
        <h3>Second domain</h3>
        <p>Epilepsy added. Pipeline validated as domain-agnostic.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-tag timeline-tag--planned">Planned</span>
        <h3>Publication</h3>
        <p>Preprint on bioRxiv describing methodology and findings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <span class="timeline-tag timeline-tag--planned">Planned</span>
        <h3>Expansion</h3>
        <p>Additional therapeutic areas where treatment is incomplete.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
